{"tid":1224850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東大嶼研究打尖 下星期五上財會","createTime":"2019-06-15T05:13:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T05:13:59.000Z","uid":203889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"19eb71bb3b3a4d79c41ff9225585512d13012290","tid":1224850,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:13:03.000Z","msg":"【暫你老＿ 東大嶼研究打尖 下星期五上財會】<br />\n<br />\n「暫緩」修例又如何？政府趁現時火頭火勢，昨日打算將橫洲撥款強闖財會，結果被議員不斷打斷阻止。今日當TVB放風話「暫緩」修例，以為可以緩和社會氣氛，誰知最新的財委會文件，又突然直接將東大嶼5億前期研究撥款打尖上財會闖關。<br />\n<br />\n我們的立場很清晰，洗濕個頭，返唔到轉頭，以往的「研究撥款」，幾乎所有都會必做、點會研究失敗？<br />\n<br />\n--------------------<br />\n認識土盟：<a href=\"http://landjusticehk.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flandjusticehk.org&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlWWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=7604d087\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://landjusticehk.org</a><br />\n支持我們：<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/s/landjusticehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fs%2Flandjusticehk%2F&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlWWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=6d51c12f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/s/landjusticehk/</a><br />\n<br />\n土地正義聯盟 守護大嶼聯盟 Save Lantau Alliance<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2923550984382584&amp;id=183564741714569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2923550984382584%26id%3D183564741714569&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlWWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=ae792a4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2923550984382584&amp;id=183564741714569</a>"},{"pid":"c52c47c70cc4b7402f773b6fb14cd5be5842533a","tid":1224850,"uid":24897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:13:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />616重點 請廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 撤回惡法<br />\n2. 撤回暴動指控<br />\n3. 釋放被捕示威者 停止白色恐怖<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"1c9adcb0e9322573e5e5ce533a618be70c5950d0","tid":1224850,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:13:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tAbjOsC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtAbjOsC.jpg&h=b1f99ab0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}